0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"네, 네…… 야마토 씨가…… 말을 걸어 주셔서……\n처음엔…… 의상만…… 도와드리는……\n것뿐이었지만……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-me1-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"중간부터…… 다른 스태프의 일도……\n돕게 돼서…… 무척…… 공부가 됐어요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-me1-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"지금까지보다…… 연극 공연을, 즐길 수…… 있게 됐어요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-me1-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"린코","body":"하나의 세상을, 만들어내기 위해서……\n다 같이…… 이미지를 공유해서……\n조금씩…… 연극 무대가, 완성…… 돼 갔어요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"ev59-me1-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"sou